Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.82,0:00:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro... joined Daybreak?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.13,0:00:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Mirei!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.99,0:00:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That must have been frightening.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.75,0:00:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.68,0:00:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I have canceled tomorrow's prayer visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.64,0:00:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We can spend the day relaxing, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.16,0:00:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.19,0:00:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I fully understand that you are suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.93,0:00:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You have done nothing wrong, Miss Mirei.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.45,0:00:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Those in the wrong are \Nthe malicious outsiders who--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.93,0:00:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.47,0:00:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand. You are feeling on edge, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.68,0:01:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,At a time such as this, \Nthe best thing to do is rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.43,0:01:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Mirei...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.77,0:03:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Name\NReminiscence
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.19,0:03:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It is time for afternoon tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.19,0:03:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,How long do you intend to sit in that manner?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.94,0:03:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.86,0:04:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Drink your tea and calm down, \Nand forget all that happened yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.45,0:04:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,There. Is that not a lovely fragrance?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.38,0:04:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You fully understand now, do you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.68,0:04:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That the outside world is unkind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.85,0:04:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The world is full of bad people.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.11,0:04:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If you stay here, by my side, all will be well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.27,0:04:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Mirei...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.08,0:04:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You should drink the tea while it is still warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.71,0:04:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.21,0:04:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.87,0:04:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow, we will bring in a new driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.43,0:04:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone reliable, who will not unsettle \Nyour emotions in the way Mr. Momoyama does.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.74,0:04:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.10,0:05:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Danji hasn't done anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.19,0:05:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Please do not refer to a servant \Nin such an overly-familiar manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.02,0:05:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He's no ordinary servant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.28,0:05:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He has taken me to all sorts of places, \Nand told me about many things I never knew!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.17,0:05:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He means everything to me, so why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.68,0:05:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Mirei, you are demonstrating \Nspecial feelings for that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.21,0:05:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But you heard which team \Nhis friends belong to, did you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.20,0:05:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Please compose yourself, Miss Mirei.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.63,0:05:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You do realize that there are many bad teams \Nwho ridicule and exclude vulnerable people?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.73,0:05:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The longer they exist, \Nthe more people will have to weep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.00,0:05:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,They made you suffer as well, \Ndid they not, Miss Mirei?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.94,0:06:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Momoyama came here to reform his life \Nafter having lead that team, Blackout.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.43,0:06:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He is currently unworthy of trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.21,0:06:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But Mr. Danji isn't like the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.23,0:06:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He stuck up for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.03,0:06:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He protected me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.40,0:06:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we rest a little longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.27,0:06:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to what I'm saying!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.89,0:06:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Clearly, you are still on edge.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.45,0:06:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,As it appears that you are still \Nunable to speak calmly, Miss Mirei,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.32,0:06:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I will prepare something else for you to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.79,0:06:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anything that you would like?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.59,0:06:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Moo-Moo Hida Dairy Parfait.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.34,0:06:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You know I asked about a drink...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.95,0:06:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you do about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.92,0:06:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'd meant for us to leave sooner,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.58,0:07:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,but I had trouble getting us away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.39,0:07:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you never change?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.04,0:07:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said, you're half-hearted.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.05,0:07:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,By trying to be a little kind to everyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.26,0:07:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,you maintain a lack of responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.43,0:07:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't make clear distinctions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.61,0:07:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You claim you'll quit, but don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.13,0:07:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And you don't do what you said you would!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.35,0:07:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Realize what matters. Be an adult, for once!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.89,0:07:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't manage that, \Ndon't do anything uncalled-for!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.16,0:07:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Danji...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.43,0:07:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Danji...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.90,0:08:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Danji...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.89,0:08:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Where would you like to go, miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.51,0:08:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I am fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.81,0:08:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop laughing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.18,0:08:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,They are guests staying at this hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.77,0:08:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall I have them return to their room?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.44,0:08:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.79,0:08:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.91,0:08:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.07,0:08:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking for somebody!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.72,0:08:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Danji!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.25,0:08:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Danji! Mr. Danji!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.27,0:08:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Danji!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.80,0:08:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Danji!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.77,0:08:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirei!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.92,0:08:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Danji...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.99,0:08:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirei!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.16,0:08:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.64,0:08:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.69,0:08:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. ... Danji...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.73,0:09:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.99,0:09:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate people like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.18,0:09:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...who go away without a word!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.97,0:09:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.56,0:10:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I know they won't be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.27,0:10:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.80,0:10:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The front gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.68,0:10:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.32,0:10:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you on the verge of tears?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.82,0:10:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's more fun with more than just two.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.37,0:10:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,They knew that I was with Daybreak, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.04,0:10:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course they won't show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.76,0:10:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Still... they made a promise, yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.84,0:10:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, let's go, already.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.48,0:10:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.84,0:10:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with just the two of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.73,0:10:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If they're not there, then two is enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.56,0:10:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll just go where we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.00,0:10:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,They definitely won't show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.77,0:10:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.21,0:11:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So you believe in them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.85,0:11:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.98,0:11:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,...Danji...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.99,0:11:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm dropping the "Mr." part.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.79,0:11:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.57,0:11:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Danji, can I make just one request?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.32,0:11:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Walk more slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.32,0:11:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.57,0:11:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so noisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.09,0:11:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I can hear everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.59,0:11:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh, I just can't handle things today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.20,0:11:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I mentioned before that \NI had a big brother, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.30,0:11:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.91,0:11:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was little, he'd put \Na good-luck charm on my ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.97,0:12:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.93,0:12:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,...at one point, I moved to Sendai.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.17,0:12:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,My big brother told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.27,0:12:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,...that there was a big festival \Nnear the new house we'd be living in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.85,0:12:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But Mommy said I couldn't go, \Nbecause it was dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.59,0:12:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,However, my big brother snuck me out, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.77,0:12:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so happy, going to my first festival \Nwith a bunch of pocket money.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.66,0:12:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.19,0:12:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The shrine we arrived at \Nwas the wrong place entirely!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.04,0:12:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I could just barely hear the festival music.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.92,0:12:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The venue was probably close by.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.84,0:12:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But ultimately, we didn't know where it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.49,0:12:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,My purse was heavy with coins,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.93,0:13:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and I could only barely hear the festival music,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.19,0:13:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,which all left me feeling \Nincredibly miserable, somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.93,0:13:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But when my big brother covered my ears,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.48,0:13:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,the agonizing noises all went away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.24,0:13:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Even now, I remember that light roar, \Na sound belonging only to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.39,0:13:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Anytime I felt unhappy, \Nhis good-luck charm would drown it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.25,0:13:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Know what I heard from Haruka?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.77,0:13:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She'd told me that my big brother died.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.00,0:13:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This was while I was in grade school.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.31,0:13:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.11,0:13:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It was an accident, she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.16,0:14:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.01,0:14:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to tell her this:
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.34,0:14:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirei was able to make it to her first festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.56,0:14:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Moreover... with the person most precious to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.37,0:14:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew they'd show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.21,0:15:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.02,0:16:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,...that I left you all startled yesterday, \Nwith no explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.07,0:16:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You must have your reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.38,0:16:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.06,0:16:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going to ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.79,0:16:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the sense in asking?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.85,0:16:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is a festival day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.14,0:16:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I once read somewhere that festivals are for \Nforgetting the pain and suffering of daily life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.83,0:16:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,A day just for laughing and dancing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.61,0:16:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So for today, it shouldn't matter \Nwhether we're enemies or allies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.15,0:16:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I'm not sure if what I read was true...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.91,0:16:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.65,0:16:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you mind us visiting the festival with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.58,0:16:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.46,0:16:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.80,0:16:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And Tohya said he'd treat us to candied apples!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.71,0:16:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd you say that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.71,0:16:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Buttered Potatoes  -  Yo-Yos
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.71,0:16:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Chicken Skewers - Stir Fry Noodles
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.42,0:16:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Pancake Fish - Baby Cakes
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.67,0:17:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So, uh... are you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.20,0:17:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anything that sounds good to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.74,0:17:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine. Go join the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.07,0:17:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.02,0:17:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you mind if I joined you \Nin getting something to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.90,0:17:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... I'll read out the names of \Nthe food stalls as we pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.41,0:17:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Stir fry noodles, candied apples...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.45,0:17:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So, how's work, lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.31,0:17:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gotten used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.07,0:17:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,How are the old-timers \Nat the construction site doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.30,0:17:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamura's been bedridden \Never since his back seized up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.29,0:17:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What, it happened again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.98,0:17:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Bro! Get me that bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.73,0:17:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not a kid, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.34,0:17:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But you gave a bear to Yu-yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.55,0:17:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oof. When you put it that way, \Nit's hard to say no.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.70,0:17:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,They're having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.01,0:17:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It was always like that at Blackout, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.91,0:17:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,With Danji around, everyone's always laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.43,0:18:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You could say that Danji's presence \Nis what brought everyone to Blackout.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.89,0:18:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, it's still fun there now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.59,0:18:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that why you're being malicious? 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.15,0:18:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't exclude me. 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.66,0:18:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, we didn't mean to...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.15,0:18:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.17,0:18:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.70,0:18:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's awfully crowded here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.39,0:18:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, Miss Mirei!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.96,0:18:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.53,0:18:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Mirei...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.38,0:18:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Mirei, you can't go walking off by yourself--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.79,0:18:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If so, then give him back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.91,0:18:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Give Danji back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.07,0:18:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Mirei!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.39,0:18:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirei!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.99,0:19:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop laughing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.34,0:19:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop laughing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.97,0:19:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.84,0:19:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.82,0:19:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Big... Brother...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.81,0:19:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.04,0:19:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.25,0:19:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying, Danji?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.28,0:20:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Does everyone except me know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.70,0:20:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody in the Minae family knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.84,0:20:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Only Haruka knows about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.51,0:20:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.47,0:20:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.78,0:20:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone knows!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.76,0:20:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You've come waltzing back, intent on\Ntaking the Minae family away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.77,0:20:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not why!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.33,0:20:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not why...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.67,0:20:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why did you come back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.89,0:20:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,After all I've suffered in your place, \Nas the successor to the Minae family!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.04,0:20:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Having to be the good girl, \Nenduring the adults who ignore me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.56,0:20:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It was all because you were dead, and yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.99,0:20:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet, it was all a lie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.29,0:20:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ultimately, you ran away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.34,0:20:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.75,0:20:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You thought you could just keep on lying to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.46,0:20:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And in the end, I'm all alone! Utterly alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.47,0:20:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate this! I hate this, I hate this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.47,0:21:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough! Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.61,0:21:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I have nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.43,0:21:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No great past like yours, no fun memories,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.11,0:21:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,no place where I belong, \Nno people I can believe in, nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.42,0:21:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It was all a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.90,0:21:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.22,0:21:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Please believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.20,0:21:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.94,0:21:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you go again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.18,0:21:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll always be by your side!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.81,0:21:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't lie to you ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.61,0:21:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never betray you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.44,0:21:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.98,0:21:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Please believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.55,0:21:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Please believe me! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.82,0:21:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Please... believe... me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.53,0:21:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.04,0:21:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.81,0:21:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Never ever?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.60,0:21:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.90,0:21:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it kills you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.09,0:21:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.98,0:21:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, never let me go...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.95,0:21:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,...even if it kills you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.53,0:22:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And throw away everything \Nbelonging to Danji Momoyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.96,0:22:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Blackout... friends... teammates...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.90,0:22:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Danji has an awful lot, doesn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.74,0:22:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Throw it all away.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.58,0:22:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And choose me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.74,0:22:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Nadatsugu, my brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.21,0:22:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Mirei!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.97,0:22:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.08,0:22:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop calling him that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.95,0:22:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He's my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.33,0:22:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Your... brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.26,0:22:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Danji is Miss Mirei's... older brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.25,0:22:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,His name isn't Danji.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.91,0:22:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother was lying to you all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.59,0:22:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Lying, and playing at being a "big bro".
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.73,0:23:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother's real name... is Nadatsugu Minae.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.61,0:23:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And because I am Arthur, I must be decisive. 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.46,0:23:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,First, I will state my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.18,0:23:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Mirei Minae, from Daybreak.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.09,0:23:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What is your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.49,0:23:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.22,0:23:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Yu-yu Kondo, from Blackout.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.14,0:23:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I am going to... destroy you, and Blackout.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.69,0:25:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,A Piece of Soul
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.78,0:25:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Check Out My Card!\NA Piece of Soul
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.49,0:25:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,A Piece of Soul
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.15,0:25:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Danji!\NA Piece of Soul
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.03,0:26:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, I'm gonna introduce \Nmy deck's awesome card, Diabolos Striker, Lyle!\NA Piece of Soul
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.62,0:26:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, I'm gonna introduce \Nmy deck's awesome card, Diabolos Striker, Lyle!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.51,0:26:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,First and most importantly, \Nyou've gotta check out its flavor text!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.04,0:26:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,"I won't let anyone stop this strike of mine--!" 
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.56,0:26:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, burning hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.75,0:26:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This dude's totally intense!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.51,0:26:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.41,0:26:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What's its crucial skill?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.13,0:26:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, of course it's a cool and hot skill \Nthat brings across Lyle's relentless manliness!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.43,0:26:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,To Be Continued 
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.65,0:26:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Next Episode 
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.42,0:26:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Megumi vs Haruka\NRecollection 
